  "name": "Pyramid Puzzler",
  "shortName": "pyramid-puzzler",
  "description": "<i>Pyramid Puzzler</i> is a 1 - 2 player game designed to teach multiplication.<br><br>Two players attempt to reach the top of a pyramid by correctly answering multiplication questions.  There are 3 levels of question difficulty., and each player gets 10 seconds to correctly answer a question.  If they are successful, they get to move 1 position.  If they answer incorrectly, their opponent gets to move 2 positions.  If two players land on the same position, the player who was there first gets a chance to answer another question.  If they are correct, their opponent is bounced backwards, otherwise they are bumped backwards.  ",
